						               													<description>This supplement adds a variety of campaigns for the Panzer Korps operation scale WW II rules, though the order of battle and maps are sufficiently detailed that they could be used for other games if desired.  Twenty scenarios spanning the West Front, East Front, North Africa, and Pacific theaters from 1935 through 1944.  Each scenario includes forces and maps for the first battle of the campaign.  Additional battles in the campaign are based on the results of the previous battle(s).  For example, if the offense breaks through the defense in one battle, the next battle may be fought with the defender employing a delaying action with hasty defenses.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Typical table sizes are 6'x4', although table sizes up to 12' are used for larger campaigns.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Expands:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Panzer Korps:  Divisional Level Warfare 1936-1945&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
